{"tid":2321674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁頌恆－「光復香港 時代革命」發起人之一","createTime":"2020-12-11T16:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T06:33:44.000Z","uid":154486,"like":262,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"0091bac0340bd1e2d3259b264200316abcf0f6f8","tid":2321674,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:29:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2019/07/28/197626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2019%2F07%2F28%2F197626&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=90d54bca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2019/07/28/197626</a><br />\n<br />\n關於「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n<br />\n呢句係梁天琦喺2016年初參加新界東補選時嘅口號。其實喺2016年1月初梁天琦宣布參選時，仲未有呢句口號。當時宣布參選嘅記者招待會上嘅新聞稿公布嘅選舉口號係「知行合一，世代革新。」<br />\n<br />\n喺2016年嘅一月下旬，<br />\n<span class=\"navy\"><span class=\"xx-large\">天琦約左青年新政嘅召集人<strong><ins>梁頌恆</ins></strong>同另一位成員</span></span>上當時本民前位於土瓜灣嘅辦公室商討選舉策略。<br />\n<br />\n（因當時本民前缺乏選舉經驗，所以好多時都會向有區選經驗以及時有合作嘅青年新政請教）因為覺得當時嘅口號唔夠搶耳，立場亦唔夠鮮明，所以當晚幾個人就喺Office嘅露台構思新嘅選舉口號。<br />\n<br />\n其實參與補選嘅主要目的係宣場本土理念同宣傳本民前，而本民前當時最為人熟悉嘅就係佢哋2015年喺屯門、沙田、元朗、上水等地區發起嘅光復行動，所以就想喺選舉口號上用「光復」嘅字眼，提醒選民本民前係喺街頭抗爭爭取香港人應有權利嘅抗爭者。因為係新界東補選，Brainstorm 嘅過程有諗過用「光復新東」，但因為嗌起黎唔夠順口，最後就再放大到用「光復香港」，聽起黎搶耳，講起黎又順口。<br />\n<br />\n至於口號嘅後半部份則係由原本嘅「世代革新」進化而成。用「革命」一詞切合本民前嘅政治理念同鮮明嘅組織定位。而當晚則喺「時代革命」同「世代革命」嘅選擇之間，未有決定。最後天琦思前想後，覺得革新同改變唔係取決於人嘅年齡，而係取決於人嘅思想有冇追上時代嘅步伐，所以決定以「光復香港，時代革命。」作為選舉口號。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"navy\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><br />\n巴治奧<br />\n多謝你既付出<br />\n多謝你叫醒左我<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZGm9X4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZGm9X4.png&h=dfe0a563&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e2fb3b2f88306841538e8624d1bf1e9689bf62b","tid":2321674,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fa801f36e57de83544dac14e78042f5e992cc7","tid":2321674,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55ff133bc2c949aae5944d44885624faae6fca0","tid":2321674,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c020909f2aedab50306ea270b473ab78233b42e","tid":2321674,"uid":158546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41186ad50d9abf68106ab9c739e30e6905c10e50","tid":2321674,"uid":37516,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:33:21.000Z","msg":"佢不止叫醒左人<br />\n大部分時間比人當係鬼都默默做自己野<br />\n<br />\n寧願比人鬧係鬼都唔做分化撚"},{"pid":"dd04cb005130afba0ec9ba9a905b798b8d2af60e","tid":2321674,"uid":154486,"like":133,"dislike":3,"score":130,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:33:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">的士gif係TVB剪接出黎</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67r6BFy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67r6BFy.png&h=8d4be12c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Li1qyS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Li1qyS.png&h=55a6635c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據會員屎路比分析<br />\n關於的士片<br />\n<br />\n當晚開live 我唔記得係咪冼志 （2016年10月定11月左右）<br />\n成個flow 我印象大概係咁<br />\n<br />\n1. 出速狗<br />\n2. 大隊一齊跑+ 撤<br />\n3. 當時退到某個位班速狗冇追上去live 個陣 cctvb 條友close up 影緊大頭<br />\n4. 巴治奧見到行過去屌隻tvb契弟話「要影大頭就影佢」<br />\n5. 大隊散得7788<br />\n6. 巴治奧見散得7788之後先坐的士走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後cctvb 班賤種剪走3-5<br />\n變成好似一出速狗巴治澳就即刻飛的咁<br />\n但事實係至少有30-60mins 時間差<br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n張gif 最初係cctvb 作撚完<br />\n然後熱狗班契弟周街send 發大黎講<br />\n<br />\n認真睇一睇再諗一諗都知一定剪過<br />\n第一下show 出黎起碼過一百人係度跑緊<br />\n第二下巴治奧坐的個下附近乜人都冇<br />\n唔通個100人 一秒之間唔見曬咩"},{"pid":"aea8fa6ae78ef42766244b7a72de189e7f3222cd","tid":2321674,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0091bac0340bd1e2d3259b264200316abcf0f6f8","tid":2321674,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:29:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2019/07/28/197626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2019%2F07%2F28%2F197626&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=90d54bca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2019/07/28/197626</a><br />\n<br />\n關於「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n<br />\n呢句係梁天琦喺2016年初參加新界東補選時嘅口號。其實喺2016年1月初梁天琦宣布參選時，仲未有呢句口號。當時宣布參選嘅記者招待會上嘅新聞稿公布嘅選舉口號係「知行合一，世代革新。」<br />\n<br />\n喺2016年嘅一月下旬，<br />\n<span class=\"navy\"><span class=\"xx-large\">天琦約左青年新政嘅召集人<strong><ins>梁頌恆</ins></strong>同另一位成員</span></span>上當時本民前位於土瓜灣嘅辦公室商討選舉策略。<br />\n<br />\n（因當時本民前缺乏選舉經驗，所以好多時都會向有區選經驗以及時有合作嘅青年新政請教）因為覺得當時嘅口號唔夠搶耳，立場亦唔夠鮮明，所以當晚幾個人就喺Office嘅露台構思新嘅選舉口號。<br />\n<br />\n其實參與補選嘅主要目的係宣場本土理