 出速狗<br />\n2. 大隊一齊跑+ 撤<br />\n3. 當時退到某個位班速狗冇追上去live 個陣 cctvb 條友close up 影緊大頭<br />\n4. 巴治奧見到行過去屌隻tvb契弟話「要影大頭就影佢」<br />\n5. 大隊散得7788<br />\n6. 巴治奧見散得7788之後先坐的士走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後cctvb 班賤種剪走3-5<br />\n變成好似一出速狗巴治澳就即刻飛的咁<br />\n但事實係至少有30-60mins 時間差<br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n張gif 最初係cctvb 作撚完<br />\n然後熱狗班契弟周街send 發大黎講<br />\n<br />\n認真睇一睇再諗一諗都知一定剪過<br />\n第一下show 出黎起碼過一百人係度跑緊<br />\n第二下巴治奧坐的個下附近乜人都冇<br />\n唔通個100人 一秒之間唔見曬咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:19:28.000Z","msg":"佢係最後先走嗰個"},{"pid":"2019766016347ff75ee1a0e0c6a044d98c089001","tid":2321674,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bd1e94a50fe1c11a000864dd089b8f49aca34b","tid":2321674,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:35:31.000Z","msg":"立法會本土派第一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb6bc080b0ba091914cf3d3b3928fdf3ac64e70","tid":2321674,"uid":35752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d88596b71771dd4e06058595e86c3bb3702c1f45","tid":2321674,"uid":53000,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:02:46.000Z","msg":"仲記得新東補選時<br />\n有人話梁天埼係鬼<br />\n<br />\n換屆選舉時<br />\n有人話梁游係鬼<br />\n<br />\n啲鬼依家<br />\n一係就坐監<br />\n一係就流亡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:40:26.000Z","msg":"成日屈人係鬼嗰班甩皮甩骨人黨反而可以留喺立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692b234b00ddeec0da2c3a6c636da8a1199970ed","tid":2321674,"uid":272580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d916ae45dee90d9f1a221b3e38cee83e2c7215bf","tid":2321674,"uid":226955,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"dd04cb005130afba0ec9ba9a905b798b8d2af60e","tid":2321674,"uid":154486,"like":133,"dislike":3,"score":130,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:33:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"